{"tid":1821113,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[PS4] Gundam Battle Operation 2 [57] 革命烽火已經燃燒 出擊吧!香港人!","createTime":"2020-01-12T04:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T04:37:59.000Z","uid":210672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5e5744e8c7b6610cf3204be2ead8e50dc15aa856","tid":1821113,"uid":210672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:27:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHY4YpP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHY4YpP.jpg&h=fddba512&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日任<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AGnapyZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAGnapyZ.png&h=0afdd444&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下格團團規(違規者踢)<br />\n1.3日唔上就踢，日日清<br />\n(上唔到請講聲，冇人知你幾時棄game)<br />\n2.理性討論<br />\n3.下格歐洲人<br />\n4.尊重<br />\nhea團沒有團規<br />\n日文官網: <a href=\"https://bo2.ggame.jp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbo2.ggame.jp&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXZwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=926a3594\" target=\"_blank\">https://bo2.ggame.jp</a><br />\n中文官網 : <a href=\"https://bo2.ggame.jp/hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbo2.ggame.jp%2Fhk%2F&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXZwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=c7f971cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://bo2.ggame.jp/hk/</a><br />\n遊戲Wiki: <a href=\"https://www65.atwiki.jp/battle-operation2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww65.atwiki.jp%2Fbattle-operation2&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXZwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=d14e927e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www65.atwiki.jp/battle-operation2</a><br />\n新手注意<br />\n溫馨提示:咩都唔識就搵𡃁妹玩下訓練先<br />\n順手拎部200cost神器訓練吉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QV6wq3t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQV6wq3t.png&h=316827ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KEKMn0X1MHk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKEKMn0X1MHk&d=uClJ75VMDgyJ2T8QnpTVXZwtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=c375d0ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KEKMn0X1MHk</a><br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n <br />\nFAQ<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點解我成日斷線<br />\nA. 為己為人, 自殺 對戰請用Lan 線<br />\n<br />\nQ. 間中會遇到隱形敵人/無敵/黑畫面, 係咪有外掛?<br />\nA. 掛你老母 有咁嘅情況其實係Lag 機引致, 官方已經公佈咗短期內會有update 去解決問題 好似已經fix咗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ. 今集有無EN限制?係咪好似上集兩個鐘先回1粒EN?<br />\nA. 今集廢除咗EN, 玩真人體力制, 燃燒自己嘅小宇宙啦<br />\n<br />\nQ. 有無分Server? 用港定日psn 好?<br />\nA. 今集係國際Server, 港日psn 都係一齊玩, 但之前GBON轉Server 前科, 所以用日psn應該會安全啲<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點解無得同朋友一齊開房玩<br />\nA. 除咗Ranking mode之外, 其他2個mode 都可以邀朋友<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點樣用支援炮擊<br />\nA. 佔點之後會見到有個數字倒數, 當倒數到0之後就可以落機call 炮擊, 威力極大如善用可以一擊逆轉戰況<br />\n<br />\nQ. 機/武/Parts 點樣升lv?<br />\nA. 用DP直接買下一lv, 如果未有得買即係未夠軍階<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點樣放炸彈<br />\nA. 1. 基礎戰先有得放<br />\n2. 去到基地搵 [ ! ]個ICON<br />\n3. 行到正確嘅位置,就會有話框叫你長按O 裝炸彈<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點樣出滾地 (緊急迴避)<br />\nA. 如果你部機有&rdquo;緊急迴避制御&ldquo; skill就可以連按兩次Boost掣使出急迴<br />\n(Default setting 即係連按X)<br />\n<br />\nQ:部機lv1用唔用到lv5武器？<br />\nA:無限場所有lv都得 <br />\n限cost場要跟機lv, 高過部機過就降到你所持有嘅武器當中與機體同級或以下lv<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點樣出反格<br />\nA. 對方出格鬥時按三角撞埋去, 判定時機請自行練習<br />\n<br />\nQ. 格鬥點出二連斬三連斬<br />\nA. 機體要有&rdquo;格鬥連擊制御&ldquo; Skill, lv1可以2hit, lv2可以3hit<br />\n<br />\nQ. 點解有人可以斬完又斬好似無硬直?<br />\nA. 運用Boost Cancel 技巧就可以解除攻擊後嘅硬直(包括火箭炮, 加農炮, 格鬥, etc), 方法係攻擊後立即輕按Boost step 走<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手製SETTING建議<br />\n打之前改改手製個SETTING<br />\nDefault 用X加速搞到加速其間好難轉方向<br />\nR1轉武R2射又令人好易轉錯武<br />\n所以改成<br />\nR1射<br />\nR2轉武<br />\nL1加速<br />\nX跳<br />\n其他不變<br />\n<br />\nCredit: 浴缸裡的貓, One.For.All, 高熱火焰, 闇之大精靈<br />\n<br />\n怎麼才算好泛機隊友? #曲<br />\n1.) 開場時散開衝, 唔好係我前面阻住我衝<br />\n2.) 到主戰場企係我前面擋彈, 等我定好位先好走<br />\n3.) 我射時唔該有後眼自動遠離我射線<br />\n4.) 我比人射時唔該有NT感應BOOST過黎幫我擋彈<br />\n5.) 擋完彈之後好馬上急回彈開等我可以零秒反擊<br />\n6.) 有格機打我你地要血肉長城保護我<br />\n7.) 就算因為保護我而死, 唔該死遠D免得爆炸D光影響我, D煙唔該飄遠D唔好影響我開鏡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"014098e9f8ae8e8534bbbc5738537dfa776a176c","tid":1821113,"uid":36445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:28:12.000Z","msg":"埋完地雷咪又自己開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05bb45704bbfa6524645606ce3067ae17a24e7cd","tid":1821113,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:28:45.000Z","msg":"我無留意係我中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"119b95e17a572823b486eb6254b646b5c4e70721","tid":1821113,"uid":210672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:28:47.000Z","msg":"慢咗"},{"pid":"ce0bb7ce7a7f9e43f78af1185c57e649eca9709a","tid":1821113,"uid":133791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:30:41.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"f5ba376f83f27b13fe2df9d80183813c979996d7","tid":1821113,"uid":220985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:32:11.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"9cb45bdf4a3ff8b892b3e63645ffa2d058b13a3f","tid":1821113,"uid":210672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:36:21.000Z","msg":"[PS4] Gundam Battle Operation 2 [57] 謝謝辣台妹<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1821114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1821114</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"690779c12a4f188c5d96465bb36f4f73d23b3e50","tid":1821113,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T04:37:03.000Z","msg":"打到2000分都唔滿嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你班友又唔留頭比target 食"},{"pid":"77a601c071e987195da60a9254d23a1336927090","tid":1821113,"uid":2